<h1>The input readonly attribute</h1>

<p>The readonly attribute specifies that an input field should be read-only (cannot be changed):</p>

<form action="/action_page.php">
  <label for="fname">Read only:</label><br>
  <input type="text" id="fname" name="fname" value="John" readonly><br>
  <label for="lname">Disabled:</label><br>
  <input type="text" id="fname" name="fname" value="John" disabled><br>
  <input type="submit" value="Submit"><br>
  <label for="datemax">Min and Max:Enter a date before 1980-01-01:</label>
  <input type="date" id="datemax" name="datemax" max="1979-12-31"><br><br>
  <label for="username">Username REQUIRED:</label>
  <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>

</form>

